###Block: Arcanist Exploits
Invoke Primal Magic				KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Invoke Primal Magic			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																				ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20																																																								DESC:When an event within 30 feet of the arcanist would trigger a chance for a primal magic effect, the arcanist can spend 1 point from her arcane reservoir as an immediate action to increase the chance to 100%%.
Redirect Primal Magic			KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Redirect Primal Magic		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																				ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DEFINE:RedirectPMagicRadius|0		BONUS:VAR|RedirectPMagicRadius|20+(5*floor(classlevel("Arcanist")/2)))																											DESC:If the arcanist triggers a primal magic event, she can spend 1 point from her arcane reservoir as an immediate action to redirect the event. The event occurs at a location of the arcanist’s choosing within a %1-foot radius. This radius expands by 5 feet for every 2 arcanist levels she has.|RedirectPMagicRadius
Resist Primal Magic				KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Resist Primal Magic			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																				ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20			DEFINE:ResistPMagicBonus|0			BONUS:VAR|ResistPMagicBonus|(classlevel("Arcanist")/2)							TEMPBONUS:PC|SITUATION|Spellcraft=Avoid triggering primal magic|ResistPMagicBonus				DESC:When attempting to cast spells in an area infused by primal magic, the arcanist can spend 1 point from her arcane reservoir as part of the casting to gain a +%1 bonus on Spellcraft checks to avoid triggering a primal magic effect.|ResistPMagicBonus

###Block: Greater Arcanist Exploits
Create Primal Event				KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Create Primal Event			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.ArcanistGreaterExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																															ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20																																																								DESC:The arcanist can twist the magic of an area, forcing primal magic events to occur there. As a standard action, she can spend 2 points from her arcane reservoir to create a 10-foot-by-10-foot area of primal magic at a point within 30 feet. The arcanist can increase the size of the area to 20-foot-by-20-foot by spending 2 additional points from her arcane reservoir. The primal magic effect remains for 1 minute.
Consume Primal Event			KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Consume Primal Event			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.ArcanistGreaterExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural			PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Arcanist Exploit ~ Swift Consume											ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20																																																								DESC:When the arcanist encounters a primal magic event, as an immediate action she can attempt to consume its power, as the consume spells class feature. The arcanist must succeed at a Fortitude save equal to 10 + the CR of the primal magic event, or she fails to consume the event and is staggered for 1d4 rounds. The arcanist must have the swift consume exploit to select this exploit.
Create Primal Event				KEY:Arcanist Exploit ~ Create Primal Event			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ArcanistExploit.ArcanistGreaterExploit.SpecialQuality.Supernatural			PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Arcanist Exploit ~ Counterspell											ASPECT:ChildAbility|Arcanist Exploits			SOURCEPAGE:p.20																																																								DESC:The arcanist can attempt to counter a primal magic event as if counterspelling a magical effect. This requires a Spellcraft check with a DC of 10 + the CR of the primal magic event. If she succeeds, the event is dispelled per dispel magic. The arcanist must have the counterspell exploit to select this exploit.

